Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:21.87,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どんな未来も　ふたりで見たかった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:28.41,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どんな想いも　伝わる距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:35.13,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}君の旅立ち　覚悟してたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:41.30,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)\blur2}背中押す言葉　声にならない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:48.06,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,750)\blur2}最後につよく　抱きしめたあと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:53.61,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}ぬくもりと同じだけの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:03:01.53,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哀しみが　僕の心つつんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:07.66,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur2}優しくなるための　サヨナラ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:14.33,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕だけの幸せをくれたひと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.92,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつかまた会えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:22.72,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}本当の君が見つかるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:28.43,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑顔忘れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:21.87,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}無論何種未來 都想一同見證
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:28.41,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}有你伴我身畔 思緒才能傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:35.13,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}早已有所準備 你會踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:41.30,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)\blur2}幾欲衝口而出 終究未能表達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:48.06,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,750)\blur2}直至分別之際 深深擁抱過後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:53.61,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}與溫暖同等份量的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:03:01.53,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哀傷將我的心包覆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:07.66,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur2}為了變得溫柔 就此別過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:14.33,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}令我獨佔幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.92,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直至再會之日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:22.72,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直至覓得真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:28.43,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}莫要忘記笑顏

Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和島尾君去過的最後的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獨自看到這片景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本以為自己會哭出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到卻很平靜 好失望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為地方好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是因為比較投緣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那棵樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很友好的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說 容易爬的樹看起來比較友好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你不這樣想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如這邊的粗枝友好的伸出了手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面的樹枝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎在招呼人來坐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐上去肯定很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棵樹肯定對人很友好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花的這種想法是怎麼來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從畫書裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多半是因為我讀過愛樹的女人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人變成根了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:04:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被女人所愛的樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要展現出好的方面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個勁的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後長成大樹 上了年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這一期間 女人一直在樹的旁邊生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但女人三千歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樹根生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人無論如何都想治好它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃過樹根後 被毒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但轉世後 成為了樹根的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大團圓結局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 女人死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為服毒了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這能算是大團圓結局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但女人變成樹根了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好胡來的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作者是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 是她創作的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是小學生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽所屬的「媽媽排球隊」的成員之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流行用布做畫書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和排球有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 用打補丁的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然寫了這麼沉重的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當年好喜歡那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼題目？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂喜歡就這點程度？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可能的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想把島尾君的壞細胞全都吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會吃壞肚子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說會轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先把背包放下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pass
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棵樹果然很友好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒出息的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨你怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 六花好野蠻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瘋丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前沒學過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爬樹 在體育課上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是山裡的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城裡的孩子沒有學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒上過體育
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 一次也沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒傳過接力棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是克拉拉大小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}克拉拉：《阿爾卑斯山的少女》中生病的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到運動白癡的島尾君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為他是在開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人 找零 找零！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您忘記找零了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑步姿勢好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個小學生遠足時也能爬的小山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是島尾君登上過的 地球上的最高峰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊踏鬆軟的土地 仰視天空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能轉世 我想做只蟬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果帶道具來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊走 你指什麼花就收集來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能做成花束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次帶來吸水海綿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在河邊開花卉展覽會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法實現的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越積越多 如同繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我死後 能吃一點我的骨頭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有完成約定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燕子… 沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己… 沒變成青蛙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭變成那種角色了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是童話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說都是過去讀過的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼呢 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰是大叔啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼看都是大叔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要用外表大小來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 因為我們是小孩大小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你能理解我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 午安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正忙著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒空理你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧 我累了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要搬那個玻璃棺材吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道就不要問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 公主睡在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡姿也好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我也想休息～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界真是亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？ 大家都是認真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是認真的 不是開玩笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以確認一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來吻醒公主的王子可以是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為大叔們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是王子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要用那張臉一口拒絕我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前途有望 年輕誠實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王子沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你全都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡有望了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是充滿希望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有在可以看到未來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在什麼都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比王子健康吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事很有利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在從小就不健康的人看來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又能怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長不會看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡就是喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在種我的夏雪草的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擅自挖墓碑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那把…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舊鏟子的主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是島尾君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之所以不回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你是島尾君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是因為你是葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的跑步姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會摔倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像雷一樣劈劈啪啪打落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到動不了為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在特等席上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那乾燥的掌心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若無其事的表情背面的真意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有激情澎湃的花的編排
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我追隨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君喜歡用顏色強的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我自己過去也分析過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確實喜歡使用鮮艷的紅色和橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很單純
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能喜歡使用不被用來探病的花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道他本人有沒有自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在定期住院前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君總喜歡大量使用照得眼疼的鮮亮顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像作法一樣把家裡佈置得像個花田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花的編排是面鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代表不甘心的刺眼的粉色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實得很
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的份 已經蓋好章了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁我還能討論萬一時的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要盡量先安排好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和姐姐也有商量過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以自己決定是否關店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然滿嘴謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只有和草與泥土打交道的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒法隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是店裡 還是庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明都流露出無盡的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是從地攤上淘來的奇形怪狀的花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是從百元店買來的應付事的茶碗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感情如飛雪般簌簌而落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種獨一無二的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充斥在店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拋棄時卻交給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算把答案交給對方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能只會讓人不知怎麼辦喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎樣告別
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣說有點犯規
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我沒有選擇的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我投伴你老到步履蹣跚 一票
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能處理我全部東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有六花一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能把捨棄的任務交給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這樣的自己 真的好沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須全部扔掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明總有一天會忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻要特意去做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君做的東西 選的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord0\shad0\c&HEFF1EF&\move(75,36,75,450,0,7800)}最\N愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些… 全是島尾君的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身有股樟腦味…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是… 島尾君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從什麼時候開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本不打算做到這一步的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只想在這座山上埋掉自己的部分骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就全部讓給他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在不守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就更有惡人的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 自從無法復生的一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就已經不是人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺已經遲了呢 一切的一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今雖然有點晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是不是蟲子少了點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為畫起來太麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈… 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然被認定為王子了？

Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:31.95,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,750)}いつも夢のなかでは　あなたは笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:39.16,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}どうして　ねえ　消えないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:43.25,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}I gave you everything. You gave me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:46.92,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(750,500)}きっと　いつまででも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.84,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}You're everything, still my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:53.05,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}愛しているんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:22:05.48,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}真夏に降った雪のような　それは儚い奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:15.78,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}あなたに出会わなければ　こんなに切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:23.46,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}胸を締め付けることもなかった　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:35.80,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}あなたに出会えなければ　強さも優しさも　知らずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:45.02,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}目を閉じれば　すぐそこに　あなたがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:31.95,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,750)}在夢中 你總帶著笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:39.16,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}為什麼 揮之不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:43.25,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}我給了你全部 你給了我何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:46.92,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(750,500)}我堅信 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.84,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}你是我的全部 仍是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:53.05,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}我都深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:22:05.48,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}彷如夏日飛雪 那是如夢似幻的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:15.78,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}若沒有邂逅你 便不會如此五味雜陳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:23.46,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}不會心如刀絞 即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:35.80,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}若沒有邂逅你 便不知何謂堅強與溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:45.02,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}合上眼簾 近在咫尺 有你相伴
